    "Soy ridículamente afortunado."

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez17.rpy:414
translate spanish jez17_d6bd107e:

    # "I lean over and kiss her. After a moment, she wakes up and starts kissing me back."
    "Me inclino y la beso. Al cabo de un momento, se despierta y empieza a devolverme el beso."

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez17.rpy:417
translate spanish jez17_2da1db6a:

    # det "What time is it?"
    det "¿Qué hora es?"

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez17.rpy:418
translate spanish jez17_cc6dd810:

    # pc "Almost seven."
    pc "Casi las siete."

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez17.rpy:419
translate spanish jez17_59cedcbe:

    # det "Damn... almost time to start getting Javi ready for school."
    det "Joder... ya casi es hora de empezar a preparar a Javi para el colegio."

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez17.rpy:420
translate spanish jez17_3b7ec1e5:

    # det "I thought maybe there would be time for a little dick before work..."
    det "Pensé que quizá habría tiempo para un poco de sexo antes del trabajo..."

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez17.rpy:421
translate spanish jez17_c092911e:

    # det "Maybe next time."
    det "Quizá la próxima vez."

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez17.rpy:424
translate spanish jez17_d6186c3d:

    # "Jez gets up and starts getting Javi ready for school."
    "Jez se levanta y empieza a preparar a Javi para el colegio."

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez17.rpy:425
translate spanish jez17_bd5da20c:

    # "I have to go get ready for school too, so I tell them goodbye."
    "Yo también tengo que irme a preparar para el colegio, así que les digo adiós."

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez17.rpy:426
translate spanish jez17_6ad487d2:

    # jav "Bye, [pcname]!"
    jav "¡Adiós, [pcname]!"

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez17.rpy:427
translate spanish jez17_66a78b77:

    # det "Have a good day. See you later."
    det "Que tengáis un buen día. Nos vemos luego."

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez17.rpy:430
translate spanish jez17_97718355:

    # "What an amazing night. I could see myself being with Jez forever. It could be a nice life."
    "Qué noche tan increíble. Me veo pasando el resto de mi vida con Jez. Podría ser una vida bonita."

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez17.rpy:431
translate spanish jez17_9ac3f5c1:

    # "I know I'll have to decide eventually."
    "Sé que al final tendré que decidirme."

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez17.rpy:432
translate spanish jez17_a9509397:

    # "But not today."
    "Pero hoy no."

